ytran NEWS

2026-04-14  Version 1.1

  * Channel URL support: auto-detect @handle, /channel/, /c/, /user/
    URLs and expand via yt-dlp.
  * Batch mode with circular retry queue and AIMD backoff for channels,
    --fix, and multiple video URLs.
  * TTY-aware countdown timer between retried requests.
  * Resume-on-restart: batch progress saved to queue_state table;
    Ctrl-C saves position cleanly via SIGINT handler.
  * Credit exhaustion detection (HTTP 402) with actionable message.
  * Descriptive error markers stored in DB for failed downloads.
  * New flags: --max-backoff, --min-delay, --initial-delay.
  * Removed ytchan and ytfix helper scripts (folded into ytran).

2026-03-08  Version 1.0

  * Initial release.
  * Fetch YouTube transcripts via transcriptapi.com.
  * Clean and format transcripts with Claude.
  * Generate short and full summaries.
  * SQLite database with XDG-compliant storage.
  * Channel name/handle tracking.
  * Batch fix mode for backfilling missing fields.
